  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -0.213885373953014         -5.8201          -134.22          -561.56
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.064795260499615          1.7632            40.66           170.12
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.035647766728604         -0.9700           -22.37           -93.59
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
  Total Pauli Repulsion:                 0.156744801857885          4.2652            98.36           411.53
 (Total Pauli Repulsion =
  Delta E^Pauli in BB paper)

